Package: strokeSankey
Title: Sankey Diagram for Stroke Risk Factors in Blacks
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Soumya", "Chava", email = "chavasoumya.ao@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    This package recreates a Sankey-style visualization of the population
    attributable risk (PAR) of stroke risk factors in Black populations
    across multiple years. The package provides a reusable ggplot2-based
    function for generating the Sankey diagram and includes the dataset
    used for the visualization.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
